HELP LINK

make_link( ________leftitem, _________rightitem )
    Establishes a link between a "left" and "right" pair of items.
    Any item can have one left-linked value and one right-linked
    value, the latest link taking precedence.


break_link( ________leftitem, _________rightitem )
    Breaks an established link between a "left" and "right" pair
    of items.  The two items must be already linked.


leftlink( ____item ) -> _____item'
_____item' -> leftlink( ____item )
    A property that, given the right item of a linked pair, returns
    the left item.


rightlink( ____item ) -> _____item'
_____item' -> rightlink( ____item )
    A property that, given the left item of a linked pair, returns
    the right item.


link_undef
    The value returned by default by leftlink and rightlink.  Can
    be used for breaking individual links.
